

spin a server with : npm run start

follwing URL has been used to test REST API.

curl -X GET  http://localhost:8081/items

curl -X GET  http://localhost:8081/items/1

curl -X PATCH -H "Content-Type:application/json" -d {\"name\":\"Pears\",\"id\":1} http://localhost:8081/items/1

curl -X POST -H "Content-Type:application/json" -d {\"name\":\"Pears\",\"id\":1}  http://localhost:8081/items

curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8081/items/1